I’m always trying to find the best shoes to support my feet during my workouts so when I found out that an Indian fitness brand has created running shoes with carbon plated soles - I had to get my hands on them! 

Here’s my honest review: loved the shoes, super breathable, they were very stable, helped propel me during my runs. I also noticed my muscle fatigue was lower after my run. 

I would recommend this shoe from @hrxbrand 💯
